summary: If you guys don't know me already, and for some of you. You know how passionate I am about promoting artist who deserve more...
body:
If you guys don’t know me already, and for some of you. You know how passionate I am about promoting artist who deserve more followers and notice. Not only that, I myself is apart of the struggling art community. So, here I go again to tag artist who deserve recognition.

@hell-o-softie

@ragehappyaccidents

@yulichuli

@jg-sylph (this is my art account!)

@pizzabit

@mxdeer

@miffxn

@pluvae

Unfortunately, those are the only artist I know that need/deserve recognition. They’re art is wonderful and I hope they get a good fanbase for themselves.

Also, yes. I added myself because I’m not going to shy away saying, “Oh, my art is good I guess. Thank you for liking it,,,” No, there is a time where you have to own your art and say, “Hella! I’m good at this and I’m going to show the world I am.” You are great people with many talents and should be proud of your works. It’s not narcissistic to think you deserve recognition now and again! Hey, you can even tag writers, cosplayers, and many people you think who deserve to get noticed.

So reblog and tag the people who deserve the attention. And remember, reblogs are better than likes!

Edit: I made @reblogs-for-strugglingartists account!
